dataset.title: A new genus and species of whiptail armored catfish (Siluriformes: Loricariinae) from southern Venezuela

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Provenzano-Rizzi, Francisco (2023): A new genus and species of whiptail armored catfish (Siluriformes: Loricariinae) from southern Venezuela. Zootaxa 5315 (4): 315-328, DOI: 10.11646/zootaxa.5315.4.2, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5315.4.2
